NAME
    RTx-QuickUpdateUserComments - [One line description of module's purpose
    here]

INSTALLATION
    "perl Makefile.PL"
    "make"
    "make install"
        May need root permissions

    Edit your /opt/rt4/etc/RT_SiteConfig.pm
        Add this line:

            Set(@Plugins, qw(RTx::QuickUpdateUserComments));

        or add "RTx::QuickUpdateUserComments" to your existing @Plugins
        line.

    Clear your mason cache
            rm -rf /opt/rt4/var/mason_data/obj

    Restart your webserver

